 a solid way to kill a cleric.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/udarkith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darkith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Member</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/8/02 12:39:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://asgarthvanguard.com/images/avcrest.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Battleground Tactic: Killing Clerics.</span><hr size=1> High lvl vs. Cleric.<br><br>One on One, a smite cleric owns.<br><br>If you run up to melee ( which we do ) you get a face full of mez, the cleric backs off a bit, stuns you and then nukes you to death.<br><br>9 second stun, 300+ point 3 second casts, I only have about 1100 hit points at 50 non buffed...<br><br>I believe the best chance to survive one on one cleric encounters ( talking equal lvls here: 50's ) is to run away after the stun wears off cause you probably won't get to them before they nuke you dead and if you do get to them then they still have instant heals...<br><br>If you want to kill clerics, bring friends.<br><br>Truth be told, Skalds are not a very good solo RvR class.  It's in groups that we really shine. <p>-----------------------------------<br><b>Darkith - lvl 50 Troll Skald</b><br><a href="http://asgarthvanguard.com"><b>[ Asgarth's Vanguard ]</b></a><br><b>Iseult</b></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/udarkith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darkith</A> at: 5/8/02 12:43:19 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/utheblackdogg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>theblackdogg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 8